<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About | Employee TaskBoard</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet" />

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e, #0f3460);
        color: #fff;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .about-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 3rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }

      .about-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      }

      h1 {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #00b4d8;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .btn-glow {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00b4d8, #0077b6);
        border: none;
        color: #fff;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .btn-glow:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #48cae4, #0096c7);
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00b4d8;
        color: #fff;
      }

      footer {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #aaa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="about-card">
      <h1>About Employee TaskBoard</h1>
      <p>
        <strong>Employee TaskBoard</strong> is a productivity web application
        designed to simplify task management for teams and organizations. Built
        using <strong>Node.js</strong>, <strong>Express.js</strong>,
        <strong>MongoDB Atlas</strong>, and <strong>EJS</strong>, it provides a
        clean and intuitive interface for employees and administrators to manage
        daily operations efficiently.
      </p>

      <p>
        Admins can manage employee data and task assignments, while employees
        can track their own tasks and performance. It’s lightweight, responsive,
        and focused on productivity.
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-glow mt-4">⬅ Back to Home</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
      © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TaskBoard | Empowering Teams Efficiently
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
